---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { href } from "../lib/url";
---

<BaseLayout title="找不到頁面">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-[1180px] px-8 py-[120px] text-center">
    <div class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[2px] text-accent">404 · Not Found</div>
    <h1 class="mb-4 mt-3.5 font-serif text-[52px] font-medium text-ink">這一頁不見了</h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-[44ch] text-lg leading-[1.65] text-text">
      你要找的攻略可能還沒整理、或網址有誤。回首頁從分類或影片總覽重新找找看吧。
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
      <a
        href={href("/")}
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-[10px] bg-brand px-[22px] py-3 text-[15px] font-medium text-ivory no-underline shadow-[0_0_0_1px_var(--brand)]"
      >
        回首頁
      </a>
      <a
        href={href("/videos")}
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-[10px] bg-surface-2 px-[22px] py-3 text-[15px] font-medium text-ink no-underline shadow-[0_0_0_1px_var(--border-strong)]"
      >
        影片總覽
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
